prodNameC: 常盈雄烯二酮免疫放射試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
A. Androstenedione Standards: (Lyophilized)
  One vial, labeled A, containing 0 ng/mL. And rostenedione, and five vials, labeled B-F, containing concentrations of approximately 0.30,1.00,3.00 and 10.00 ng/mL (0.34-34.50 nmol/L) and rostenedione are buffer-based, with sodium azide as a preservative.
  *DSL-3800 (500 Tubes) contains three sets of standards
 B. Androstenedione [I-125] Reagent: (YELLOW)
  One bottle, 55 mL, containing <5 μCi (185 kBq) of [I-125]-labeled androstenedione in a protein-based buffer with sodium azide as preservative.
  *DSL-3800 (500 Tubes) contains five bottles of reagent.
 C. Anti-Androstenedione-Coated Tubes: (METALLIC GOLD)
  One hundred (100) plastic tubes each, with rabbit anti-androstenedione immunoglobulin immobilized to the inside wall of each tube.
  *DSL-3800 (500 Tubes) contains five hundred (500) tubes each.
 D. Androstenedione Controls: (Lyophilized)
  Two vials, Levels I and II, containing low high concentrations of androstenedione are buffer-based with sodium

efficacy: 利用放射性體外酵素免疫定量方法檢測臨床標本血漿/尿液中Androstenedine的定量測定。
